sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Chain
    participant Memory
    participant PromptTemplate
    participant LLM

    User->>Chain: "What is my name?"
    Chain->>Memory: load_memory_variables({"input": "What is my name?"})
    Memory-->>Chain: {"history": "Human: Hi I am Alice\nAI: Hello!"}
    Chain->>PromptTemplate: Fill {history} and {input} placeholders
    PromptTemplate-->>Chain: Full prompt assembled
    Chain->>LLM: Full prompt with history injected
    LLM-->>Chain: "Your name is Alice."
    Chain->>Memory: save_context(input, output)
    Memory->>Memory: Append to history / update summary / update entities
